mp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;是咁的，我係一個二十歲嘅準魔法師。<br />\n<br />\n有一日係巴士有個女仔坐我左邊<br />\n成架車得我哋兩個<br />\n<br />\n佢吃緊拉麵</blockquote>&amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我膽粗粗咁問佢可唔可以比一條拉麵我食&amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;<br />\n點知佢成碗面蓋係我頭上&amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我講左句野</blockquote><br />\nmay I fuck you?</blockquote><br />\n她曰：Just do it</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「整整石化」巴士司機道。</blockquote><br />\n然後個巴士司機就石化咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n石化完仲爆開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n威力太大炸死咗個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為咗忘記呢段傷心嘅回憶，我將記憶引到儲思盤。</blockquote><br />\n儲思盤自行燒毀"},{"pid":"6e01e971d60d22899ce5d0d367ab82c61f21b0b9","tid":20561,"uid":43725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我終於成為入門魔法師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開始養第一隻怪物&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n有一日係巴士有個女仔坐我左邊&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n佢食緊烏冬&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我膽粗粗咁問佢可唔可以比條烏冬我食&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n點知佢成碗面蓋係我頭上&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n宜家我有一碗麵，佢有一碗烏冬&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n點知巴士司機講咗句「去去無氣酒」&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n喺我面前即刻出現左支無氣酒&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n見到啲酒，我就諗起一句對聯&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n上聯係 今天的事今天做&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n下聯係 唔想做就唔撚做&amp;amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n好似唔係 同酒、麵、烏冬有關嘅</blockquote><br />\n上聯係  有酒有麵有烏冬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下聯係 無波無腳無閪窿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後個巴士司機把撚化左"}]}